responses.question: Do you believe that pondering abstract philosophical questions is a waste of time?
responses.response_open: Gaston: "Absolutely! Pondering abstract philosophical questions is for weak-minded fools who have nothing better to do. responses.question: Are you very intrigued by things labeled as controversial?

responses.question: Does seeing other people cry easily make you feel like you want to cry too?

responses.question: Do you usually stay calm, even under a lot of pressure?

responses.question: Are you very sentimental?

responses.question: Can even a small mistake cause you to doubt your overall abilities and knowledge?
responses.response_open: Gaston: Doubt? Doubt is for weaklings and fools! I never make mistakes, LeFou. I am the epitome of perfection in every way. My abilities and knowledge are unmatched by anyone. So, no, a small mistake would never cause me to doubt myself. I am Gaston, after all.

responses.question: Are you more inclined to follow your head than your heart?

responses.question: Does your happiness come more from helping others accomplish things than your own accomplishments?

responses.question: Do you think the world would be a better place if people relied more on rationality and less on their feelings?

responses.question: Can your mood change very quickly?

You see, when you're as exceptional as I am, you can't afford to leave anything to chance. So, yes, I always have a backup plan for a backup plan. It's what separates the true winners from the rest."

responses.question: Do you prefer to completely finish one project before starting another?
responses.response_open: Gaston: "Finish one project before starting another? LeFou, my dear friend, I am a man of many talents and pursuits. I don't limit myself to just one thing at a time. I thrive on taking on multiple endeavors and conquering them all with my unparalleled skill and determination. Why settle for one when I can excel in everything I do?"

responses.question: Do you like to use organizing tools like schedules and lists?
responses.response_open: Gaston: Organizing tools? Schedules and lists? Ha! Who needs those when you have the charm and wit of Gaston? I don't waste my time with such trivial matters. I simply go with the flow and let my natural talents guide me. After all, when you're as exceptional as I am, everything falls into place effortlessly.

responses.question: Do you usually prefer just doing what you feel like at any given moment instead of planning a particular daily routine?
responses.response_open: Gaston: "Well, LeFou, a man like me doesn't need to plan his daily routine. I simply follow my instincts and do what I feel like at any given moment. Planning is for those who lack the confidence and charm to seize the day. I am a man of action, always ready to pursue my desires and conquer any challenge that comes my way. So, no need for a routine when you have the charisma and strength of Gaston!"

responses.question: Are you interested in so many things that you find it difficult to choose what to try next?
responses.response_open: Gaston: "Interested? Ha! I am the epitome of excellence in all things. There is no need for me to choose, for I excel at everything I set my mind to. Whether it be hunting, fighting, or charming the ladies, I am the best at it all. No one can compare to my talents and accomplishments."

responses.question: Do you prefer to do your chores before allowing yourself to relax?
responses.response_open: Gaston: "Chores? LeFou, my dear friend, I have people to do my chores for me. I am far too important to waste my time on such menial tasks. Relaxation is my birthright, you see. I deserve to be pampered and catered to at all times."

responses.question: Do you often end up doing things at the last possible moment?
responses.response_open: Gaston: LeFou, my dear friend, I am a man of action, always ready to seize the moment and make things happen. But sometimes, you see, I like to keep the suspense, to keep everyone on their toes. It adds a certain thrill to the chase, don't you think? After all, no one fights like Gaston, and no one plans like Gaston either. So, rest assured, everything will fall into place at the perfect moment.

responses.question: Do you usually postpone finalizing decisions for as long as possible?

Like a hunter patiently waiting for his prey. So, no need to rush, my loyal companion. The decision will come when it comes."
